Defensive End Mathias Kiwanuka Agrees With Giants on Contract, NYT Reports

-- B y   L a r r y   S i d d o n s
-- 
2011-07-28T18:12:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/defensive-end-mathias-kiwanuka-agrees-with-giants-on-contract-nyt-reports.html
Defensive end Mathias Kiwanuka
agreed on contract terms to return to the  New York Giants , the
New York Times reported.  The newspaper, without citing where it got its information,
said the deal is expected to be short term and loaded with
performance incentives.  Kiwanuka was limited to three games last National Football
League season because of a neck injury.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  